### 1. 회원가입 - 이메일 인증번호 발송
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/verification/email/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "target": "badbergjrr@naver.com",
  "purpose": "SIGNUP",
  "type": "EMAIL"
}

### 2. 이메일 인증번호 확인
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/verification/email/check
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "target": "badbergjrr@naver.com",
  "code": "330979",
  "purpose": "SIGNUP",
  "type": "EMAIL"
}

### 3. SMS 인증번호 발송
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/verification/sms/send
Content-Type:  application/json

{
  "target": "01012345678",
  "purpose": "SIGNUP",
  "type": "SMS"
}

### 4. SMS 인증번호 확인
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/verification/sms/check
Content-Type:  application/json

{
  "target": "01012345678",
  "code": "1234",
  "purpose": "SIGNUP",
  "type": "SMS"
}

### 5. 회원가입
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users/sign-up
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usrId": "testuser",
  "usrNm": "테스트사용자",
  "pwd": "password123! ",
  "orgCd": "SEOUL_N_GWANAK"
}

### 6. 로그인
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usrId": "testuser",
  "pwd": "password123!"
}

### 7. 회원 정보 수정 (로그인 필요)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/users/update
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "newUsrNm": "변경된이름",
  "newEmail": "newemail@example.com",
  "newSms": "01087654321",
  "newPw": "newpassword123!"
}

### 8. 아이디 중복 확인
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/exists/user-id?usrId=testuser

### 9. 이메일 중복 확인
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/exists/email?email=test@example.com

### 10. 아이디 찾기
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/find/user-id
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usrNm": "테스트사용자",
  "email": "test@example.com"
}

### 11. 비밀번호 찾기
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/find/password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usrId": "testuser",
  "email": "test@example.com"
}

### 12. 비밀번호 재설정
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/find/password/update
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pwd": "newpassword456!"
}

### 13. 로그아웃
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/logout